{"title":"phpunit","date":"2019-07-04T00:00:00.000Z","link":"post/phpunit","tags":["phpunit"],"categories":["program"],"updated":"2019-07-04T00:00:00.000Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://phpunit.de\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PHPUnit</a>是一个面向PHP程序员的测试框架，这是一个xUnit的体系结构的单元测试框架</p>\n<h2 id=\"Install\">Install<a href=\"post/phpunit#Install\"></a></h2><p>我们用一个 <a href=\"http://php.net/phar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PHP Archive (PHAR)</a> 来包含你需要使用的PHPUnit，可以从这里<a href=\"http://phar.phpunit.cn/phpunit.phar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">下载</a>它，使其可执行，并把它放到你的 <code>$PATH</code> 里, 如:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://phar.phpunit.cn/phpunit.phar</span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod +x phpunit.phar</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo mv phpunit.phar /usr/<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>/bin/phpunit</span><br><span class=\"line\">phpunit --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"Used-in-phpstorm\">Used in phpstorm<a href=\"post/phpunit#Used-in-phpstorm\"></a></h2><p>Languages &amp; Frameworks  -&gt;  PHP  -&gt; Debug  -&gt; Test Frameworks</p>\n<p>Path to phpunit.phar. -&gt; /usr/local/bin/phpunit</p>\n","prev":{"title":"upgrade-mac-php-version.md","link":"post/upgrade-mac-php-version.md"},"next":{"title":"laravel-envoy","link":"post/laravel-envoy"},"plink":"https://spaco.github.io/post/phpunit/","toc":[{"title":"Install","id":"Install","index":"1"},{"title":"Used in phpstorm","id":"Used-in-phpstorm","index":"2"}]}